---

<Layout
  title="Admin Page for ben9583's Feedback Site"
  description="This is a private endpoint to ben9583's feedback website. Yes, it is authenticated. No, there are no bugs."
>
  <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
    <main class="main-content ml-4 mr-4 py-8 max-w-xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Admin</h1>
      <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
        This is an administrative page for ben9583 to run the website. You've
        probably ended up here by mistake (or not?). Use one of the links in the
        navbar above to get where you need to go.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
        Rest assured, there are no bugs with this authentication :)
      </p>
      <form method="POST" class="form-grid">
        <div><label for="username" class="mr-2 text-lg">Username:</label></div><Input
          id="username"
          name="username"
          placeholder="Enter username here..."
          type="text"
          required
        />
        <div><label for="passkey" class="mr-2 text-lg">Passkey:</label></div><Input
          id="passkey"
          name="passkey"
          placeholder="Enter passkey here..."
          type="password"
          required
        />
        <div><Input type="submit" value="Submit" /></div>
      </form>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .form-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 5fr;
    row-gap: 1rem;
    margin-right: 10rem;
  }
  .form-grid > * {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
</style>
